Hi Ramon,

FWIW here's what I get when I run code chunk fdfmutex2 from the 
OncoSimulR.Rmd vignette on kjohnson (Mac arm64):

 > set.seed(1)

 > s2fd <- oncoSimulIndiv(afe4,
+????????????????????? muEF = mtfd,
+????????????????????? model = "McFL",
+????????????????????? onlyCancer = FALSE,
+????????????????????? finalTime = 40,
