Subject: Re: Branch RELEASE_3_16 unavailable for MoonlightR package

There is no RELEASE_3_16 branch yet.  Bioc 3.16 is still considered devel; release branches are only created at release time.  Do NOT create it yourself; this is done by the core on git.bioconductor.org at release time.  To update devel you would push to master.

All of this is very well documented at
http://contributions.bioconductor.org/git-version-control.html#git-version-control<http://contributions.bioconductor.org/git-version-control.html#git-version-control>


